<lb ed="T" n="0896b28"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0896b28"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000005377">河東懸甕寺</placeName><persName key="A008813">金和尚</persName>傳</head><p>
<lb ed="T" n="0896b29"/><persName key="A008813">釋金和尚</persName>者，姓<name>王氏</name>，<placeName key="PL000000004810"><placeName>西河</placeName><placeName>平遙</placeName></placeName>人也，所生之<pb ed="T" n="0896c" xml:id="T50.2061.0896c"/>
<lb ed="T" n="0896c01"/>地<placeName key="PL000000004802">猪坑村</placeName>。幼而魁岸<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1572"/>，為人魯質<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2453"/>。所作詭異，
<lb ed="T" n="0896c02"/>與平人不類。於<placeName key="PL000000048295">嵩巖山</placeName>出家。其後身裁一
<lb ed="T" n="0896c03"/>丈，腰闊一圍<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2454"/>，言事多奇差<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2455"/>。終後如在，鄉人
<lb ed="T" n="0896c04"/>供祭之，乞願皆遂人意。<placeName key="PL000000006221">西河</placeName>至<name>稽胡</name><ptr target="#n1891"/>皆鄭
<lb ed="T" n="0896c05"/>重焉。</p>
